  "reviews": [
    {
      "text": "Really pleased with these painters. They came out promptly to quote and were easy to deal with from the start. Managed to fit me in at short notice, which was a big help.\n\nTurned up on time each day, kept everything tidy, and the standard of work was excellent. The finish is high quality and exactly what I was after.\n\nPricing was very reasonable for the level of work delivered. Also just genuinely nice, straightforward guys to have around. Would definitely use again.",
      "reviewer": "nic",
      "rating": 5
    },
    {
      "text": "Really hard to find top decorators - Chris and the lads were great.\nHe managed to fit me in for a quote then bedroom paint / wallpaper, communication was really good, excellent finish and cleaned all up after.\nWouldn’t hesitate to use Chris again and highly recommend. Thanks !",
      "reviewer": "N",
      "rating": 5
    },
    {
      "text": "Wow 🤩 from a bit dated looking shelves unit into a luxurious boutique hotel look! I love it! The olive 🫒 green paint and finish looks stunning! Super professional, excellent price. Definitely recommend. Thank you 🤩",
      "reviewer": "Sylvia",
      "rating": 5
    },
    {
      "text": "Chris and the lads did my sons room today n I have to say they did a fantastic professional job n tidied up after themselves aswell really impressed well done lads would recommend to anyone",
      "reviewer": "Gemma",
      "rating": 5
    },
    {
      "text": "Great job by Chris and his team at AC Painters painting exterior of terrace house in Crosby for me this week. Looks great and very happy to recommend.",
      "reviewer": "Helen",
      "rating": 5
    }
  ],
